Package org.gvsig.exportto

Exportto library API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExporttoManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's business logic.
    ExporttoService
    This service is used to export a source FeatureStore to a target FeatureStore.
    ExporttoServiceFinishAction
    Action that can be executed at the end of the export process.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExporttoLibrary
    Library for API initialization and configuration.
    ExporttoLocator
    This locator is the entry point for the Exportto library, providing access to all Exportto services through the ExporttoManager .
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExporttoException
    Generic exception thrown in the Exportto API when the exception or error may be dealt by the program or the user of the program which is a client of the Exportto API.
    ExporttoServiceException
    Exception thrown when there is an error getting a Exportto message.

Package org.gvsig.exportto Description

Exportto library API.

It allows to get new Exportto and get their text.
